{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_04_01",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 1話 気付いてほしい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……素敵。ここが当日の会場なんですね\nでも……今更ですけど、本当にいいんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… It's beautiful. So this is the venue for the day‚ huh?\nBut… I know it's a bit late to ask‚ but is this really okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃から言ってくれたんじゃないか\n心配しなくていいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as you said to yourself‚ Kotono.\nDon't need to worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……私、まだ高校生ですよ？\nその……結婚なんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I'm still a high school student‚ you know?\nUm… Marriage and all that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃なら大丈夫だよ。なんせ遙子さんのお墨付きだしな\n琴乃ならきっと……ウエディングドレスを着こなせるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You'll be fine‚ Kotono. After all‚ you have Haruko-san's approval.\nI'm sure Kotono will be able to pull off a wedding dress beautifully.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そう……だったら、嬉しいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… If that's the case‚ then I'm happy tho…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日前のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、どうするかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I wonder what to do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3633.333333299994,
          "startTime": 48.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\nどうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ {user}-san. Good job today.\nWhat's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5966.6666667,
          "startTime": 58.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、お疲れ様\n迷ってる仕事があってな……これなんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ hello.\nI have a job I'm undecided about… It's this one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "これは……\nアイドルを広告塔にしたウエディング企画ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this…\na wedding project that uses idols as a model?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "これって、アイドルがウエディングドレスを\n着るってことですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ this means the idol\nwill wear a wedding dress‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。ぜひ星見プロのアイドルに\n出演していただきたいって依頼を受けたんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. I received a request for\na collaboration with Hoshimi Pro's idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "依頼……受けないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren't you going to accept the offer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それが、先方からは「黒髪が良く似合うデザインなので\n出来れば黒髪の人がいいです」と言われてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the request mentioned‚\n\"We prefer someone with black hair because it suits the design.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "黒髪が似合う、ウエディングドレス……\nなるほど、なるほど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A wedding dress that suits black hair…\nI see… Indeed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、月ストは撮影日にライブがあるし……\nそれで、サニピなら遙子さんがいいかと思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ Moon Tempest has a live on the shooting day…\nSo I thought Haruko-san would be suitable for Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですね\n確かに遙子さんなら良く似合うと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nIndeed‚ I think Haruko-san would look great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだろ？　だけど、ちょうどお願いしたら\n遙子さんに別の仕事の依頼が来てな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right? But just when I was about to ask her…\nShe received another job offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "ソロのお仕事……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A solo job…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "お漬物会社の広告塔になってほしいという依頼なんだ\n番組でよく漬物の話をしていたのが良かったみたいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a request to become a ambassador for a pickled vegetables company.\nIt seems they liked that she often talked about pickled vegetables on the shows.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、「私の話、地味じゃないかな？」って\n気にしてたから……お仕事に繋がって良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san was worried that her stories were too plain…\nIt's good that it led to a job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんも自分を指名してくれたって凄く喜んでたよ\nだから、ウエディングの仕事は断ることにしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san was also extremely happy that she was specifically requested.\nThat's why I decided to decline the wedding job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "あの……{user}さん\nそれなら、えっと、わ、私――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… {user}-san.\nIn that case‚ um‚ well‚ I――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5366.666666700013,
          "startTime": 154.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "おっと、悪い。誰だろう……あれ、遙子さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ sorry. Who could it be… Oh‚ Haruko-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5299.999999999983,
          "startTime": 159.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし。はい、琴乃と話してたところです\nえ？　はい、分かりました、琴乃に伝えておきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello? Yes‚ I was talking to Kotono.\nEh? Okay‚ got it. I'll let Kotono know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n遙子さんはなんて言ってたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san.\nWhat did Haruko-san say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど今話してた件だったよ。琴乃ならドレスが\n似合いそう、って俺に勧めるつもりで電話をくれたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was about the very thing we were talking about.\nShe said that wedding dresses would suit you‚ and she wanted me to suggest it to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
