      "text": "でもなぁ、琴乃はライブがあるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you have a live performance‚ right‚ Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "……ウエディング撮影が時間通りに終われば、その後の\n月ストのライブには間に合うと思いますけど。たぶん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If the wedding shoot finishes on time‚\nI think I can make it to the Moon Tempest live. Probably.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
