      "text": "本当か！？　あ、でも……いいのか？\nウエディングは女性にとって大事なものだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!? Ah‚ but… Is it okay?\nA wedding is an important thing for a woman‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそうですけど……仕事ですし\n着てみたくないことはありませんし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true… but it's still work.\nAnd I don't mind trying on the dress…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
